page1.title: Hello!
page1.content: I’m Vinay Kudari, currently pursuing MSc in Computer Science at SUNY Buffalo University. I’m a technology enthusiast who has been developing software for over 5 years and professionally for over 3.5 years. I enjoy developing technical solutions for real-world problems at scale, I’m known for writing clean, maintainable code. . I am presently an intern at Sony developing PlayStation 5 backend systems. Previously, I was one of the founding engineers for a startup in its earliest stages. I have experience managing projects with vague requirements. I graduated from National Institute of Technology, Durgapur with B.Tech in Computer Science . I’m open (Hire Me) for full time positions starting early 2023. .
